    <p>If your grill is under Twin Eagles warranty (now administered through Dometic, typical lifetime warranty on stainless burners, varies on other components), we recommend going through the dealer network first. We can assess and tell you if the failure is warranty-eligible before any out-of-pocket repair.</p>
